      "explanation": "分散式合併公式(parallel/streaming reducer 核心):mc = (n1*m1+n2*m2)/(n1+n2);vc = (n1*(v1+(m1-mc)²) + n2*(v2+(m2-mc)²)) / (n1+n2)。變數。直覺:總變異 = 群內 var 加…",
